HEADWORD: Gunnery
<hw>Gun"ner*y</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>That branch of
military science which comprehends the theory of projectiles, and the
manner of constructing and using ordnance.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

